# G005 Workflow 2 Toy Campaign

Goal: validate a minimal deterministic Workflow 2 / Ralph-style autonomous campaign loop in a newly bootstrapped project.

This campaign is local-only. It does not test production automation, provider orchestration, GitHub integration, auto-merge, deployment, live trading, paper trading, browser access, or network access.

Expected outputs:
- `docs/toy_workflow2/phase_a.md`
- `docs/toy_workflow2/phase_b.md`
- `docs/toy_workflow2/summary.md`
- one run directory under `runs/<run_id>/` with state, event, summary, STOP, and per-phase artifacts
